flowRoot.flowPara: Today, we will start a logo competition for openSUSE.Asia Summit 2019, which is going to be held in Bali, Indonesia. A logo is an essential material for the successful summit. As you have seen, the former openSUSE.Asia summits have their unique logos reflecting the communities where the summit took place. Following tradition, we have logo competition to collect great logo for this year’s summit.

text.tspan: Deadline of this contest is June, 15th 2019 (UTC 13:00)
We only accept SVG and PNG format and recommend the artist to use Inkscape for all kinds of design.
Please read the details of rules by following this link: https://s.id/oSAS-logo-competition

flowRoot.flowPara: Kompetisi logo untuk openSUSE.Asia Summit 2019 yang akan diadakan di Bali, Indonesia dibuka. Logo merupakan hal yang sangat penting untuk sebuah konferensi. Seperti diketahui bersama, openSUSE.Asia Summit sebelumnya juga memiliki logo unik yang mencerminkan komunitas tempat diselenggarakannya kegiatan.

text.tspan: Kami hanya menerima format berkas SVG dan PNG, perangkat lunak Inkscape lebih disarankan
Silakan baca detail aturan kontes yang dalam halaman berikut ini: https://s.id/oSAS-logo-competition
Kirim logo terbaik Anda ke surel: opensuseasia-summit@googlegroups.com
